===Adjective===
{{en-adj|er}}

# [[dedicated|Dedicated]] to a [[religious]] purpose or a [[god]].
#: ''I'm planning to visit the '''holy''' city of Mecca this Ramadan.''
# [[revere|Revered]] in a [[religion]].
# [[perfect|Perfect]] or [[flawless]].
# Separated or set apart from (something unto something or someone else).
# Set apart or dedicated for a specific purpose, or for use by a single entity or person.
# {{context|slang|lang=en}} Used as an [[intensifier]] in various [[interjection]]s.
#: '''''Holy''' cow, I can’t believe he actually lost the race!''

